data.description: ONLY 35 MINUTES FROM PHILADELPHIA!!!!This contemporary two-story sits quietly at the end of a cul-de-sac. With a fenced in yard, 3 beds and 2.5 baths this home is perfect for a growing family or pet lovers. The kitchen has been recently renovated and is updated with laminate flooring and stainless steel appliances. The property also has a separate laundry room, ample closet space, large family room, back patio and a primary suite with vaulted ceilings. Central air-conditioning and forced hot air make this home comfortable and practical all year round.
